00:39:40.600 --> 00:39:43.050
But Viewport width--

00:39:43.050 --> 00:39:46.180
so you can actually say, 1% of
the Viewport width, I want to

00:39:46.180 --> 00:39:47.200
move it over.

00:39:47.200 --> 00:39:50.800
So you can move a
div or element

00:39:50.800 --> 00:39:52.720
