00:39:52.720 --> 00:39:56.860
So as you think about using
absolute and relative

00:39:56.860 --> 00:40:03.710
positioning, just think in
terms of the size of the

00:40:03.710 --> 00:40:05.340
screen that you're working on.

00:40:05.340 --> 00:40:06.620
